The paper discusses a framework for optimization problems using probability distributions and natural gradients, which is a common topic in machine learning and optimization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
